<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.1">
<l>oṉṟun tēvu mulaku muyiru maṟṟum yātumillā</l>
<l>vaṉṟu nāṉmukaṉ ṟaṉṉoṭu tēva rulakō ṭuyirpaṭaittāṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟam pōṉmaṇi māṭa nīṭu tirukkuru kūrataṉuḷ</l>
<l>niṉṟa vātippi rāṉiṟka maṟṟait teyva nāṭutirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without one thing, god, world, living being, other life, anything</l>
<l>that day he created along with the four-faced one the gods, along with the world the living beings.</l>
<l>While the primeval lord is there who stays in tall Tirukkurukūr</l>
<l>with with mountain-like jewel mansions, would you seek any other god?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
